data.title: Wellington Indoor Sports Centres Ltd.
data.meta_description: New Zealand's largest indoor sports provider. Providing Wellington Based competitions for indoor netball, indoor soccer, indoor cricket and bubble soccer.

“’We had our son’s sport birthday at WIS and we were extremely happy with how it went. The staff were friendly and accommodating, and all our guests went away saying how amazing the day was. Thank you once again”
